Assignment- 1

Ø Step 1- create your account on amazon aws using root or IAM user

Ø Step 2- Then open ec2 services and click on instances and select region (asia pecific Mumbai).

Ø Step 3-Name your instance and click on window O.S and select it.

Ø Step 4- select instances types ( select t3.micro ).

Ø Step 5- now create your key pair name (key pair type should be RSA and and format .pem).

Ø Step 6- after creating your key it will be downloaded automatically.

Ø Step7- allow SSH traffic from my ip address only .

Ø Step 8- now click on launch instance.

Ø After launched your instances go to your instances and select your instance.

Ø and click on connect then click on RDP client and download remote desktop file.

Ø Now click on get password and click on upload private key.

Ø And choose your pem file and upload it.

Ø Then click on decrypt password and copy your password .

Ø Open your remote desktop file and paste your password.

Ø And click on connect .now your virtual window will be opened.
